Class QueryObjectModelFactoryFacade<S extends javax.jcr.Session>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.adamcin.oakpal.core.jcrfacade.query.qom.QueryObjectModelFactoryFacade<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the session type parameter
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.jcr.query.qom.QueryObjectModelConstants, javax.jcr.query.qom.QueryObjectModelFactory

    public class QueryObjectModelFactoryFacade<S extends javax.jcr.Session>
extends Object
implements javax.jcr.query.qom.QueryObjectModelFactory
    Wraps QueryObjectModelFactory to ensure that QueryObjectModel instances are wrapped with QueryObjectModelFacade read-only wrappers.
